{"tid":1198022,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]推到巴士、小巴、的士等交通公具的士司機罷工？","createTime":"2019-06-10T06:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T07:41:49.000Z","uid":126875,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"dc2e18271c9b7aec3c4a2a6eb7edc54adb9f9e42","tid":1198022,"uid":126875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:20:38.000Z","msg":"和理非非嘅巴絲就算唔支持勇武抗爭，都唔可以咩都唔做就咁放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勇武有勇武嘅做，和理非嘅都可以幫手諗下點推到所有公共交通公具嘅司機都一齊罷工罷駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而罷駛嘅影響力一定會比各位巴絲自願罷工罷課更強大，因為連好鍾意返工嘅廢中都會被迫停工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小妹希望大家都可以幫手諗諗計，睇下點樣可以說服各位司機大佬加入抗爭行列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲唔好繼續畀林奠個柒婆揸春袋啦好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c91fc137bd39a36cc02f42aa06ff2a5c2815e6","tid":1198022,"uid":49544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:50:19.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52eb5c0abfff51c2441a20d7e391a67fef156f9","tid":1198022,"uid":56537,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:50:24.000Z","msg":"小巴同的士狗邊有可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da3683d0868f35b17d00dd2d69a41c4412447cf","tid":1198022,"uid":1134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:52:49.000Z","msg":"我地依班巴士佬<br />\n可以話唔會罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f28e8dccac18abc4b348a11a0d6091c31a94c4dd","tid":1198022,"uid":5413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:53:45.000Z","msg":"一係按章工作?"},{"pid":"021ad84a53a8272698693bce9567b39b5ce8246d","tid":1198022,"uid":842